name: Hentai: Memory leak II
description:
In solving puzzles in Hentai: Memory leak only your memory can help you. As a reward you will receive the art of beautiful fairy-tale girls that you can’t forget.

In the game you will find:

- A variety of levels to train your memory.
- The art of a beautiful girl performed by the master of his craft LeArtNi!
- Relaxing music from composer Trauerbaum.
- Lots of fun!
